Web UI Automation Test with Gauge
=================================
Akbank Kredi Hesaplama test senaryosu otomasyonu

Scenario : Credit Calculation
-----------------------------
* Enter "https://www.akbank.com/" Akbank Home Page
* Scroll down to the bottom of the page
* Click on 'Kredi Hesaplama'
* Enter "50000"TL in 'TUTAR' field
* Choose "SİGORTASIZ" in the button
* Set VADE as "20AY" in the bar
* Click 'Hesaplama Detayları'
* Check "Masraf ve Maliyet Oranları" is opened
* Click 'Ödeme Planı'
* Check "Ödeme Planı" is opened
* Scroll down on the 'Ödeme Planı' page until 20th is seen